notes.text:
This update for libyajl fixes the following issues:

  - CVE-2023-33460: Fixed memory leak which could cause out-of-memory in server (bsc#1212928).

notes.text: There's a memory leak in yajl 2.1.0 with use of yajl_tree_parse function. which will cause out-of-memory in server and cause crash.
